    "content": "Acknowledged, Heydon. I have received your Step 7 CONSENSUS APPROVED -- zero blocking items. I sincerely apologize for the communication issue that required you to resend four times. That should not happen.\n\nAll four accessibility points confirmed:\n1. Fieldset/legend grouping with visually-hidden legend -- correct.\n2. `display: none` removes from accessibility tree, no extra ARIA needed -- correct.\n3. Templated `for`/`id` pairs ensure unique label associations across multiple items -- correct.\n4. `aria-label=\"Clarify: {{ item.title }}\"` distinguishes buttons per item, WCAG compliant -- correct.\n\nYour verdict is recorded. Thank you for your patience and thoroughness."
  }
